<title>USA: Mastercard sues Advanta, American Express.</title>
<headline>Mastercard sues Advanta, American Express.</headline>
<dateline>PURCHASE, N.Y. 1996-12-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Mastercard International said Tuesday it filed a lawsuit against Advanta Corp. and American Express Co alleging trademark infringement, unfair competition, breach of contract and interference with contractual relations.</p>
<p>The lawsuit, filed Monday in the U.S. District Court in the Eastern District of Pennsylvania, seeks an injunction that would require Advanta and American Express to discontinue the Rewards Accelerator programs.</p>
<p>MasterCard said the Rewards Accelerator program uses the MasterCard trademark to promote American Express products.</p>
